---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import { baseUrl } from '../../utils/base.ts';
---

<Layout
  title="Roadmap - UOMP"
  description="UOMP development roadmap from protocol draft to full ecosystem."
  lang="en"
  switchHref={`${baseUrl}roadmap/`}
>
  <section>
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Roadmap</h1>
      <p>From protocol draft to a complete ecosystem.</p>

      <h2>Milestone 1: Core Protocol & Reference Implementation</h2>
      <ul class="roadmap-list">
        <li><span class="status status-done">Done</span>Publish UOMP-Draft-00 specification</li>
        <li><span class="status status-done">Done</span>SQLite-based Memory Store</li>
        <li><span class="status status-done">Done</span>Auth Service HTTP API: create/grant/close/revoke sessions</li>
        <li><span class="status status-done">Done</span>Memory Guard HTTP API: read-only access filtered by tag/key</li>
        <li><span class="status status-done">Done</span>JWT Capability Token issuance and validation</li>
        <li><span class="status status-done">Done</span>Token blacklist persistence in SQLite</li>
        <li><span class="status status-done">Done</span><code>uom.json</code> Agent Manifest parsing</li>
        <li><span class="status status-done">Done</span>ERC-8004 compatible local Registry index</li>
        <li><span class="status status-done">Done</span>Generic CLI: <code>discover</code>/<code>connect</code>/<code>authorize</code>/<code>import</code>/<code>sessions</code>/<code>revoke</code>/<code>audit</code></li>
        <li><span class="status status-done">Done</span>Stock analyst Agent end-to-end example</li>
        <li><span class="status status-done">Done</span>Remote Profile + Gateway reference implementation (mTLS + remote Capability Token forwarding)</li>
        <li><span class="status status-done">Done</span>Aggregation query (`/v1/memory/aggregate`) + deletion proof API</li>
        <li><span class="status status-done">Done</span>Token claims: `allowed_fields`, `aggregation_only`, `task_bound`</li>
        <li><span class="status status-done">Done</span>Agent Manifest `data_retention_policy`</li>
        <li><span class="status status-done">Done</span>UOMP SDK Phase 1 (`UompClient`: memory / aggregate / payload / session / audit / auth / identity)</li>
        <li><span class="status status-done">Done</span>Browser Dashboard (uomp.org/dashboard/): wallet auth + Dropbox + Agent analysis</li>
        <li><span class="status status-done">Done</span>Cloudflare Tunnel integration (`uomp gateway start` one-command public expose)</li>
        <li><span class="status status-done">Done</span>Store abstraction (`IMemoryStore` interface, SQLite + EncryptedObject backends)</li>
        <li><span class="status status-done">Done</span>Cloud Relay (`apps/relay/`, CORS + rate limit + pubkey verification)</li>
        <li><span class="status status-done">Done</span>Wallet authentication (MetaMask + Argent X, PBKDF2 key derivation)</li>
        <li><span class="status status-done">Done</span>UOMP SDK Phase 1 (`UompClient`: memory / aggregate / payload / session / audit)</li>
        <li><span class="status status-done">Done</span>Stock Analyst Agent v1.0 (self-serve HTTP API + Digital Ocean deployment)</li>
        <li><span class="status status-done">Done</span>Cloudflare Tunnel integration (`uomp gateway start` one-command public expose)</li>
        <li><span class="status status-current">In Progress</span>DID / GPG / X.509 identity verification (framework present, verification strength to be enhanced)</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Milestone 2: UX, Writes & GUI Integration</h2>
      <ul class="roadmap-list">
        <li><span class="status status-next">Planned</span><code>uomp import</code> field mapping, format detection, preview</li>
        <li><span class="status status-next">Planned</span><code>uomp dry-run</code> simulated authorization</li>
        <li><span class="status status-next">Planned</span><code>uomp config</code> user preferences</li>
        <li><span class="status status-next">Planned</span>Agent write staging: writes enter <code>pending</code> until user approval</li>
        <li><span class="status status-next">Planned</span><code>uom memory review</code> approval command</li>
        <li><span class="status status-next">Planned</span>Graphical authorization panel</li>
        <li><span class="status status-done">Done</span>Graphical authorization panel (Browser Dashboard)</li>
        <li><span class="status status-done">Done</span>TypeScript SDK (`UompClient`, mTLS, aggregation, Payload, deletion proof)</li>
        <li><span class="status status-done">Done</span>Memory Store abstraction (SQLite / S3 / IPFS pluggable)</li>
        <li><span class="status status-next">Planned</span>Memory Store abstraction supporting SQLite / cloud / decentralized storage</li>
        <li><span class="status status-next">Planned</span>Audit log visualization</li>
        <li><span class="status status-next">Planned</span>Secure token delegation mode (reverse proxy)</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Milestone 3: Remote & Advanced Features</h2>
      <ul class="roadmap-list">
        <li><span class="status status-future">Future</span>Semantic retrieval (<code>query</code> endpoint)</li>
        <li><span class="status status-future">Future</span>Write version history and rollback</li>
        <li><span class="status status-future">Future</span>Policy templates (e.g., "preferences only", "preferences + public identity")</li>
        <li><span class="status status-future">Future</span>Blockchain anchoring for authorization and access events</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-btns" style="margin-top:2.5rem;">
      <a href={`${baseUrl}dashboard/`} class="btn-h1" style="background:#8B5CF6">Open Dashboard →</a>
      <a href={`${baseUrl}en/tutorial/`} class="btn-h1">SDK Tutorial →</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
